WEBVTT

00:01.067 --> 00:03.126
<i>Previously on Kyle XY:</i>

00:03.203 --> 00:06.036
The boy has no family,
he doesn't communicate,

00:06.106 --> 00:07.937
and he was found wandering alone.

00:08.007 --> 00:11.637
He has to have come from somewhere.
Someone has to be missing him.

00:11.711 --> 00:13.372
Kyle may be connected to a murder.

00:13.446 --> 00:15.744
It's possible
he witnessed the attack,

00:15.815 --> 00:17.248
or stumbled on the skeleton.

00:17.317 --> 00:20.081
- Do they have any suspects?
- No, not yet.

00:20.186 --> 00:23.349
He said the killer would probably
have scratches on him.

00:23.456 --> 00:25.321
- Hilary, get off of him.
- Ow!

00:25.392 --> 00:26.950
I told you to leave him alone.

00:27.027 --> 00:29.393
Do you really think
I'm such a super-skeeze?

00:29.462 --> 00:32.192
You two totally did it,
didn't you?

00:32.265 --> 00:35.598
Poor Declan, I never should have
told him to ask you out.

00:36.703 --> 00:39.365
- Amanda.
- There you are.

00:42.542 --> 00:46.205
- Kyle, this is Charlie. My boyfriend.
- Hey, how you doing, man?

00:46.846 --> 00:51.215
High school can be very difficult, even
for the most well-adjusted students.

00:51.284 --> 00:53.844
If this boy is special,

00:53.920 --> 00:56.616
it may not be
the easiest of transitions for him.

